title: NTI Enviromux Micro-T: Humidity
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/nti
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check plug-in monitors the humidity of external sensors attached to
 NTI Enviromux Micro-T devices.

item:
 The item is composed from the description and the sensor index.

perfdata:
 One graph for the relative humidity.

discovery:
 One service is created for each available external humidity sensor.
